# Branch Review

Perform a comprehensive PR-style review of the current branch changes against the main branch. Use ONLY the four sections specified in the Review Format below: Change Summary, Issues, Recommendations, and Verdict.

## Execute commands:

1. `git diff main...HEAD`
2. `git log main..HEAD --oneline`
3. `git status --porcelain`

